{"title":"JavaUtils","slug":"JavaUtils","date":"2022-07-24","updated":"2023-02-07","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/13372.json","excerpt":"<blockquote><p> 主要介绍了 Java 的各种工具类 </p></blockquote>","cover":null,"covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p> 主要介绍了 Java 的各种工具类 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1 id=\"IdUtil\"><a href=\"#IdUtil\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"IdUtil\"></a>IdUtil</h1><blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li> 主要介绍了各种 id 生成策略 </li>\n<li> 生成的 Id 是用不重复的 </li>\n<li>String serialNumber = IdUtil.simpleUUID();</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"TimeUnit\"><a href=\"#TimeUnit\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"TimeUnit\"></a>TimeUnit</h1><blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>TimeUnit.DAYS // 天  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.HOURS // 小时  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.MINUTES // 分钟  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.SECONDS // 秒  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS // 毫秒  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.NANOSECONDS // 毫微秒  </li>\n<li>TimeUnit.MICROSECONDS // 微秒  </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong> 转换：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>public long toMillis(long d)    // 转化成毫秒  </li>\n<li>public long toSeconds(long d)  // 转化成秒  </li>\n<li>public long toMinutes(long d)  // 转化成分钟  </li>\n<li>public long toHours(long d)    // 转化成小时  </li>\n<li>public long toDays(long d)     // 转化天   </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><strong> 延时：</strong> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>TimeUnit.SECONDS.sleep(5);</li>\n<li>TimeUnit.HOURS.sleep(1);</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"ZoneDateTime\"><a href=\"#ZoneDateTime\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ZoneDateTime\"></a>ZoneDateTime</h1><blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>ZoneDateTime.now(); 可以获得当前时间串，在 gateway 中可以配置使用 </li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"产生随机数的 2 种方法\"><a href=\"# 产生随机数的 2 种方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"产生随机数的 2 种方法\"></a> 产生随机数的 2 种方法 </h1><blockquote>\n<p> 两者均是左开右闭 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 产生 1~3 的随机数 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> System.out.println((<span class=\"type\">int</span>) (Math.random()*<span class=\"number\">3</span>) +<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"comment\">// 产生 0~20 的随机数 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> System.out.println(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Random</span>().nextInt(<span class=\"number\">20</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"UUID\"><a href=\"#UUID\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"UUID\"></a>UUID</h1><p><strong> 随机数的生成 </strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>UUID.randomUUID().toString()</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n","url":"/posts/13372/","min2read":"1","word4post":207,"prev_post":{"title":"GateWay","url":"/posts/4296/"},"next_post":{"title":"Hystrix","url":"/posts/64571/"},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"IdUtil\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">IdUtil</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"TimeUnit\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">TimeUnit</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"ZoneDateTime\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">3.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">ZoneDateTime</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"产生随机数的 2 种方法\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">4.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\"> 产生随机数的 2 种方法 </span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"UUID\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">5.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">UUID</span></a></li></ol>","categories":[{"name":"JavaStudy","path":"api/categories/JavaStudy.json","url":"/categories/JavaStudy/"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaUtils","path":"api/tags/JavaUtils.json","url":"/tags/JavaUtils/"}]}